soc.game
Class ForceEndTurnResult

java.lang.Object
  soc.game.ForceEndTurnResult

public class ForceEndTurnResult
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds the results of a call to Game.forceEndTurn(). Specifically, the resulting action type, and possibly list of discarded or returned resources.

The result object isn't intended to be conveyed over a network to clients; the server should translate it into standard SOCMessages which change game state.
